OL,4,CUK airports to fight 'silent killer'
OL,6,FMore than a dozen UK airports are now
OL,7,Fselling mobile carbon monoxide alarms,
OL,8,Fas ITV News Consumer Editor Chris Choi
OL,9,Freports
OL,11,FHudson Foley, 24, died of carbon
OL,12,Fmonoxide poisoning on holiday two
OL,13,Fyears ago.
OL,15,FOn Thursday, his mother marked a
OL,16,Fbreakthrough in her campaign to make
OL,17,Ftravel safer as, for the first time,
OL,18,Fmore than a dozen UK airports will
OL,19,Fsell mobile carbon monoxide alarms.
