OL,6,FFollowing Hudson's death, Cathy said
OL,7,Fshe thought about "how I could try to
OL,8,Fprotect other families from going
OL,9,Fthrough the horrendous time that we
OL,10,Fwill now have to go through for the
OL,11,Frest of our lives."
OL,13,F"Having a travel carbon monoxide alarm
OL,14,Fwhen you travel is your way of
OL,15,Fprotecting yourself," she said.
OL,17,F"Carbon monoxide is a silent killer,
OL,18,Fand it doesn't discriminate between
OL,19,Fage, country or standard of
OL,20,Faccommodation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
