OL,6,F"It's a very inexpensive piece of
OL,7,Fequipment that could save your life,
OL,8,Fand it definitely could've saved
OL,9,FHudson's life."
OL,11,FHudson's family believe a carbon
OL,12,Fmonoxide alarm would have prevented
OL,13,Fhis death and are convinced this small
OL,14,Fgadget can remove a huge risk for many
OL,15,Fmore holidaymakers.
