OL,6,FSafety groups say carbon monoxide
OL,7,Falarms are needed because in many
OL,8,Fcountries there's no requirement for
OL,9,Ftourist accommodation to install them.
OL,11,FStephanie Boyle from Safer Tourism
OL,12,FFoundation told ITV News: "Carbon
OL,13,Fmonoxide you cannot see, you cannot
OL,14,Fsmell, and the only way to protect
OL,15,Fyourself is to have a detector.
